be given the opportunity to show up.

Please let me know what your characters should be doing in the mean time.

I believe Straightshot, Scourge, Nightshift, Waspinator, Elita and
crew will be mapping things out.

Cyclonus and Rodimus will be trying to trace back  where these guys came from.

What will Hydras and Tuscon be doing in the mean time? I will add that
into the next post. Also Hydras called Sky Shadow over to him, was
there a purpose in that?

Anyways, I look foward to your posts and plans :)

- Preston
